page.title: 02My Neighbourhood
page.content: My neighbourhood is very nice exept for Jack because every time you play football and it goes on his grass he comes out and moans. Normally on Saturday every body is out _Julie,Tracy,Jack,Daniel and me. The nicest people are the Biddulphs because we go out with them.Alan and I play with Robert and Daniel. My next door neighbours are Lorraine and John on one side and Muriel and Ted on the other side.They are very nice. At night time when we are out we have to be quiet because there are lots of babies, but I like where I live.
